1. We are going to refactor the restock management workflow:
- we should be able to add a re-order schedule for each supplier from the manage suppliers page, the schedule should be able to be set for weekly, bi-weekly (every two weeks), monthly or custom (select dates and option to make custom recurring)
- Restpck orders submitted no longer need approval, so the workflow that requires approval is no longer needed
- The restock management page should show restock requests categorized by suppliers, all restock requests for a supplier should be listed under that supplier, the restock management page should have two tabs, one that shows the list of current restock requests listed under their supplier (so a section per supplier) and another tab that shows upcoming scheduled re-orders (it should show the next upcoming re-order scheduled for each supplier with supplier details)
