- the restock management page should have a third tab for purchase orders, where current purchase orders can be viewed and managed
- when a restock order request is submitted and their is a purchase order open for the supplier, it should be automatically added to the purchase order
- item/order receival should be done from the purchase order (so change the current workflow completely)
- a purchase order should be in open status until either cancelled or received
- the workflow should be fluid and connected, all of the pieces should be tied together so we do not have a broken and disconnected workflow